description: SHIPz are the the third phase of the MUTANtz project. On this part of our journey we explored different modes of transportation that our MUTANtz familiy will need to travel across the universes they find themselves in. This project would not be possible without the combined creativity and effort of the MUTANtz family. This is true spontaneous creativity and storytelling. Thanks for making this special.
